These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
Birthday: september, july, january, june, may, august
Flower: daffodil, amaryllis, iris, orchid, begonia, zinnia
 1. Birthday:january is in an odd position##4
 2. Birthday:august is somewhere to the left of Birthday:july##5
 3. Birthday:may != Flower:begonia##6
 4. Birthday:june is somewhere to the left of Birthday:july##5
 5. Flower:begonia is somewhere to the left of Flower:iris##5
 6. Flower:amaryllis is somewhere to the right of Flower:iris##5
 7. Flower:begonia != Birthday:july##6
 8. Flower:zinnia is in an odd position##4
 9. Birthday:september is somewhere between Flower:zinnia and Birthday:june##7
10. Flower:iris is on the left or right of Flower:orchid##3
11. Flower:zinnia is somewhere to the right of Flower:daffodil##5
12. Flower:zinnia is somewhere to the left of Flower:orchid##5
13. Flower:daffodil == Birthday:september##1
14. Flower:iris is somewhere to the left of Birthday:may##5
15. Birthday:august == Flower:orchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Birthday   | june   | september | january   | august     | july    | may   |
| Flower           | begonia | daffodil   | zinnia | orchid | iris | amaryllis |

