10. Game:monopoly is somewhere between Game:poker and Game:bridge##7
11. Game:snooker is somewhere to the left of Beverage:water##5
12. Beverage:tea is on the right of Game:whist##1
13. Game:poker is on the left or right of Game:monopoly##3
14. Game:poker is in an even position##4
15. Beverage:fanta is somewhere to the left of Game:bridge##5
16. Game:poker is on the right of Game:monopoly##1
17. Beverage:fanta is somewhere between Game:whist and Beverage:water##7

