12. Movie-Genre:zombie is somewhere between Birthday:february and Movie-Genre:spy##7
13. Birthday:october is somewhere to the left of Birthday:march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Birthday         | july   | october | january      | april | march  | february   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  | spy | comedy   | zombie | western |

